description.en: Carb0n.fi is a Singapore-based, ASEAN-focused blockchain solution funded by Owl Venture, Lancer Capital, Blockseed Capital, and Antler.co. Users can deposit crypto with Carb0n.fi and get rewarded with carbon offset NFTs as well as our native token $ZRO.
